        The Real Cost and Value of Pool Ownership in a Brisbane Home
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        A pool can be a meaningful lifestyle asset and, in some cases, a value driver at sale. It is also an ongoing operating cost and a compliance obligation. Here is how Brisbane sellers and owner-occupiers should think about the cost and value of a residential pool.
      </p>
    </div>
